4
00:00:10,840 --> 00:00:14,400
 One is we take an HTML tag and use the style attribute and

5
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:20,600
 just put those little CSS key value, you know, CSS settings right there, very close.

6
00:00:20,600 --> 00:00:23,200
 The other thing is you can put it in the background of the HTML document,

7
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:24,880
 usually in the head area.

