00:00:24,880 --> 00:00:28,640
 And the other, probably most common thing, especially when the styles get large,

9
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:31,720
 is an external style sheet that's a separately loaded file with a separate

10
00:00:31,720 --> 00:00:32,880
 request response cycle.

